Package geneticAlogrithm

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GeneticAlgorithmCall
    This is the main Class for the GA.
    It use the Genetic algorithm device provide by the watchMaker's API and the class I redefined for it.
    MySequenceEvolutionObserver
    Overwrite of the EvolutionObserver.
    SequenceCrossOver
    Class which define the CrossOver operation for an object of type Sequence
    you had to implement it to use the watchmer's GA algorithm.
    For more details, look at the watchmaker API
    SequenceEvaluator
    Class which define the Fitness function for your GA.
    you had to implement it to use the watchmer's GA API.
    Here we defined it for a Sequence object.
    For more details, look at the watchmaker API
    The principle is the following one:
    The Ga got an instance of type SequenceEvaluator and call to the fitness function.
    The fitness function lanch a praat script with the candidate and compare the formant's answer with the target's ones.
    To be sure that the fitness function wait for the answer of praat, the launch of the function put a mutex lock.
    This lock is releasw in the function getMessageFromPraat of the class GeneticAlgorithmCall when we are sure we get the answer
    SequenceFactory
    Class which define a Factory for the Sequence Object.
    As it is say in the Sequence documentation, you are not suppose to instantiate it yourself, the Ga will do it,using this factory.
    you had to implement it to use the watchmer's GA algorithm.
    SequenceMutation
    Class which define the Mutation operation for an object of type Sequence
    you had to implement it to use the watchmer's GA algorithm.
    For more details, look at the watchmaker API
